%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn166n5e.jpg&h=c05f57e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n主題📜：東歐巨變30周年集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>日期📅：17/11/2019</strong></span><br />\n時間🕐：1900～2130<br />\n地點⛩：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>備注🌟：已獲得不反對通知書</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n特別事項⚠️<br />\n👉🏻1400 ～ 1700砌牆<br />\n👉🏻招募義工一齊砌出和裝飾柏林圍牆<br />\n👉🏻2120推倒極權暴政的鐵幕<br />\n👉🏻與30年前同步，東德開放畀人民入西德，寓意希望自由民主歸回人民<br />\n👉🏻同時招募糾察幫忙維持集會秩序<br />\n👉🏻義工和糾察聯絡： @sdontstandforshit<br />\n<br />\n鐵 幕 倒 下🧱極 權 必 亡☠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1723763/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1723763/</a> <br />\n公海 Link : <a href=\"http://t.me/easterneurope1989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feasterneurope1989&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=afa83399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/easterneurope1989</a>"},{"pid":"a4321a3618ffd70b3795d7e3afa4a5221b350c01","tid":1728712,"uid":205684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1b0491f3aabd7d437111757e28fd2a8c84226f","tid":1728712,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"今日全黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"d40354f25c108a524f7b726f34afb9fefe5bbab9","tid":1728712,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"仲選票.........."},{"pid":"e3fc8875224643ad5f3a167f62fd1aad9f8b88fc","tid":1728712,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a1b0491f3aabd7d437111757e28fd2a8c84226f","tid":1728712,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"今日全黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"h